<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Tuisuogiet bang lungsiet na hi,
 Tuisanglien bang ngilneih na;
 Hinna Lal thiengtho thihna hi,
 Ka hinna tanin A thii.
 A hehpih kihetloh saka,
 Paklo kuo a um thei ding?
 Hailo hielin Van um sungin,
 Amah hengilh thei puon au.

[V2]
 2. Entie, Kalvari tang chungah,
 Thugil lopi a kekzak;
 Pathien hehpih in a tin khawm,
 A puokzak a kizen ngei.
 Pathien hehpih leh lainatna,
 Mihing lamah aluong gawm;
 Dikna leh hehpih kituok in,
 Khawvel thiemloh a chawp ui.</lyrics>
<title>CYNFAN PRYDAIN</title>
<hymn_number>69</hymn_number>
</song>